      while
      others can see them through obstacles.'
  - Name: Horror Loading Screen 03
    loadingScreenSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 06fa6d0f154ff264da5f7779bab8b573,
      type: 3}
    tip: "Tip:\nBandages aren\u2019t just for you, use them to heal your fellow\nsurvivors
      and keep the group alive!"
  - Name: Horror Loading Screen 04
